OL,3,CChris Ingram on swapping Manchester
OL,4,Cfor Monaco and his path to World
OL,5,CChampion
OL,7,FThe 30-year-old from Manchester
OL,8,Falready made history on 27 October
OL,9,F2024, when he became the first person
OL,10,Fto win both the British and European
OL,11,FRally Championship titles.
OL,13,FHe said: "There was four of us going
OL,14,Ffor the title, and to get it is a
OL,15,Fmassive relief.
OL,17,F"It's been a tough journey, but I felt
OL,18,Fso relieved to get the British one. To
OL,19,Fget the double, I'm so proud."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
