OL,3,CChris Ingram on swapping Manchester
OL,4,Cfor Monaco and his path to World
OL,5,CChampion
OL,7,FHis victory at the British
OL,8,FChampionships marks his first major
OL,9,Fwin since 2019, after the pandemic
OL,10,Fleft him unable to drive for over two
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FHe said: "I almost lost everything. I
OL,14,Fdidn't drive for two years and I had
OL,15,Fto really fight to get my career on
OL,16,Ftrack.
OL,18,F"It's been a tough journey mentally
OL,19,Fbut now I'm performing better than
OL,20,Fever and ready for what's to come."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
