OL,3,CChris Ingram on swapping Manchester
OL,4,Cfor Monaco and his path to World
OL,5,CChampion
OL,7,FDuring the pandemic, Chris was forced
OL,8,Fto move back in with his parents and
OL,9,Fquestion whether he had a future as a
OL,10,Frally driver.
OL,12,FHe said: "It was proper back down to
OL,13,FEarth. From standing on the podium
OL,14,Fwith Lewis Hamilton to being back at
OL,15,Fhome. It's been a hell of a journey.
OL,17,FNow that racing has started again,
OL,18,FChris has moved out and lives in
OL,19,FMonaco with his girlfriend.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
