OL,3,CChris Ingram on swapping Manchester
OL,4,Cfor Monaco and his path to World
OL,5,CChampion
OL,7,FHe said: "It's a dream come true. I've
OL,8,Fmet an amazing girl from Monaco, and
OL,9,FI'm living out there with her mostly.
OL,10,FIt's an amazing place to live, and
OL,11,Fthere's quite a few mancs out there."
OL,13,FChris' next big race is on 21
OL,14,FNovember, when he'll compete at the
OL,15,FRally Japan event. Beyond that, Chris
OL,16,Fis preparing for an even bigger
OL,17,Foccasion; the birth of his first child.
OL,19,FHe said: "We're expecting a baby boy
OL,20,Fin a couple of months, but she's given
OL,21,Fme permission to go to Japan.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
