OL,3,CChris Ingram on swapping Manchester
OL,4,Cfor Monaco and his path to World
OL,5,CChampion
OL,7,F"I'm definitely getting him into
OL,8,Ffootball instead of rallying. I've got
OL,9,Fhim a City shirt already."
OL,11,FChris is currently working to secure
OL,12,Ffunding to compete in the 2025 World
OL,13,FRally Championships, where he aims to
OL,14,Fbe the first British racer since
OL,15,FRichard Burns in 2001 to win the
OL,16,Fcompetition.
OL,18,FHe said: "I want to be World Champion
OL,19,Fand I know I can. It's been my dream
OL,20,Fsince I was a little boy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
